# compoundTypes

**Instance Property**

Returns the compound predicate types.

## Declaration

```swift
var compoundTypes: [NSNumber]? { get }
```

## Return Value

An array of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber] objects specifying compound predicate types. See [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSCompoundPredicate/LogicalType] for possible values.

## Information About a Row Template

- **leftExpressions**: Returns the left hand expressions for the receiver.
- **rightExpressions**: Returns the right hand expressions for the receiver.
- **modifier**: Returns the comparison predicate modifier for the receiver.
- **operators**: Returns the array of comparison predicate operators.
- **options**: Returns the comparison predicate options.
- **rightExpressionAttributeType**: Returns the attribute type of the receiver’s right expression.
